# KMIA ingest → chart bridge (Console 2)

This project is **Console 2** — Weather Ingestion & MAE Probabilities. It feeds read-only research artifacts into the Kalshi KMIA program. It is **not** the Kalshi Main Console (human live UI) or the Auto Trader Console.

Architecture: `docs/architecture/THREE_CONSOLE_ARCHITECTURE.md`

Ingest priorities:
1. Raw NDFD + ISD under `/volume2/Data/App_Development/KMIA_Ingest`
2. Processed point CSVs compatible with golden master inputs (VALID_ONLY filtering, lead-time window)
3. Manifest/checksum logging before scaling backfill

Do not treat NDFD as observed data. No live trading. No Streamlit or Kalshi order code in this repo. Active compose path: `Docker/kmia-arch-ingest/`.
